# Group Player

## Move [/move{?player_id}]
### Update location [POST]

+ Parameters
    + player_id (required, int) - The ID of the current player

+ Request (application/json)

        [
            300.50, 
            900.99
        ]

+ Response 200

        Ok. Position update accepted.
    
+ Response 400
    
        Bad request. Excessive movement detected.

## Shoot [/shoot{?player_id}]
### Fire equipped weapon [POST]

+ Parameters
    + player_id (required, int) - The ID of the current player
    
+ Request (application/json)
        
+ Response 200

