# Group Lobbies

## List [/lobbies{?player_id}]
### Retrieve all existing lobbies [GET]

+ Parameters
    + player_id (required, int) - The ID of the current player
    
+ Response 200

        [ 
            {
                "name": "lobby1",
                "current_players": ["player1", "player2"],
            },
            {
                "name": "lobby2",
                "current_players": ["player3", "player4"],
            }
        ]
            

## Create [/create{?player_id}]
### Make new lobby [POST]

+ Parameters
    + player_id (required, int) - The ID of the current player

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "name": "new-lobby",
        }
+ Response 201 (application/json)

## Join [/join{?player_id}]
### Enter existing lobby [POST]

+ Parameters
    + player_id (required, int) - The ID of the current playe

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "name": "old-lobby",
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)